It's just

36
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,118
a simple sanitization?

37
00:02:44,119 --> 00:02:44,979
You...

38
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:49,620
Why aren't you wearing this pajama?

39
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,998
Don't tell me

40
00:02:51,999 --> 00:02:53,900
you told me to wear it

41
00:02:53,959 --> 00:02:57,259
because you have a weird fetish?

42
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,558
You're just like
what the rumors had said about you.

43
00:02:59,559 --> 00:03:00,958
Your imagination is pretty wild,

44
00:03:00,959 --> 00:03:02,699
yet unrealistic.

45
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,998
Ms. Qi prepared this for you.

46
00:03:04,999 --> 00:03:06,079
It has nothing to do with me.

47
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:09,998
But don't you think
this pajama is strange?

48
00:03:09,999 --> 00:03:11,958
It feels like you're making fun of me.

49
00:03:11,959 --> 00:03:13,958
Now, as Party A, I'm requesting you

50
00:03:13,959 --> 00:03:15,678
to wear this pajama.

51
00:03:15,679 --> 00:03:16,940
You cannot wear anything else.

52
00:03:16,999 --> 00:03:17,759
What gives?

53
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:19,660
Because you assaulted me at night.

54
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,299
So, what was on your mind during daytime?

55
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:50,479
What caused you to strip
another person's clothes in your sleep?

56
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,238
I...

57
00:03:51,239 --> 00:03:53,079
I'm sure I did it

58
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,780
because I wasn't used to the bed here.

59
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,359
That's right.

60
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,118
You know this too.

61
00:03:56,119 --> 00:03:58,660
All women lack a sense of security.

62
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,180
So, you snore

63
00:04:01,279 --> 00:04:03,019
to get a sense of security?

64
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,419
That's right.

65
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:09,859
I snore as an alarm.

66
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,199
Although

67
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:14,639
this is purely
a partner-partner relationship,

68
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,319
we're a man and a woman

69
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,100
living together after all.

70
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,100
I have to stay on my toes.

71
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,219
Of course.

72
00:04:23,039 --> 00:04:26,459
That's why I came up
with a foolproof measure.

73
00:04:37,479 --> 00:04:38,740
This?

74
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,500
And this?

75
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:45,500
Are these the foolproof
measures you mentioned?

76
00:05:10,719 --> 00:05:12,380
Report your work progress to me

77
00:05:12,599 --> 00:05:14,300
before sleep.

78
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,518
How's the progress

79
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:18,779
with the bug-fixing?

80
00:05:40,359 --> 00:05:41,420
Your hand.

81
00:05:43,039 --> 00:05:44,420
Give me your hand.

82
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,358
Hurry up.

83
00:06:12,359 --> 00:06:14,500
I want to use the restroom. Hurry up.

84
00:06:25,159 --> 00:06:26,158
We're getting late.

85
00:06:26,159 --> 00:06:27,319
Pack your things.

86
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,259
We have a meeting
to attend at the studio.

87
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,439
Boss, it's just like what you predicted.

88
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,918
We found a virus

89
00:06:43,919 --> 00:06:45,259
on the external port of the server.

90
00:06:45,599 --> 00:06:47,278
Someone might've sabotaged us
on purpose.

91
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,319
Xiong,

92
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:51,398
hurry and pinpoint the exact location
of the equipment that was tampered with.

93
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:53,360
After that, retrieve
the surveillance camera footage.

94
00:06:53,919 --> 00:06:56,119
It's either

95
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,259
one of the members of the studio

96
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,819
or

97
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:03,380
someone else snuck into the studio.

98
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,119
Alright. I'll investigate it right now.

99
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,119
Can we deal with the virus

100
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,398
by performing a full system scan

101
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,659
with the antivirus software?

102
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:12,620
We only found the virus
with the full system scan.

103
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,620
And, we found out

104
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:18,259
that even the hardware was infected.

105
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,918
So? What's the result?

106
00:07:21,919 --> 00:07:24,500
The result is either we let it be

107
00:07:24,599 --> 00:07:26,420
or we wipe it clean.

108
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:30,100
It's equivalent to a factory reset.

109
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,819
If that's the case,

110
00:07:32,919 --> 00:07:34,940
my four years' worth of effort

111
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:37,459
would go down the drain.

112
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,358
Calm down for now.

113
00:07:45,359 --> 00:07:47,060
It's not that we have no way

114
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,899
to deal with infectious malware.

115
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,079
Do you have a solution?

116
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,319
One of my seniors

117
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,759
is an expert on computer viruses.

118
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:55,239
He helped resolve
some of the tougher virus issues

119
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,980
our country had encountered.

120
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,940
Should we seek his help?

121
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:07,219
Brother, don't tell me
you're talking about David?

122
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:08,960
I'm not seeing him.

123
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,760
I even fought with him
when we were still studying.

124
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,180
You still hold a grudge against him?

125
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:16,559
You can see him together with Lanyao.
I'll go and check on Dad.

126
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,380
Alright.

127
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,398
Xiong,

128
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,199
give Mr. Lin a copy
of the data files as well.

129
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,060
Alright.

130
00:08:25,039 --> 00:08:26,019
Let's go.

131
00:08:27,740 --> 00:08:29,478
Contact me in time
if you encounter any issues.

132
00:08:29,479 --> 00:08:30,420
Alright.

133
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:35,500
- Brother, I'll head to the restroom.
- Alright.

134
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,299
What's wrong?

135
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:42,679
I won't be around later.

136
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:44,419
You mustn't fall asleep.

137
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:45,799
Don't worry.

138
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,598
I'll surely uphold

139
00:08:46,599 --> 00:08:48,638
the virtuous values of office workers.

140
00:08:48,639 --> 00:08:49,799
I won't sleep

141
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,340
until the virus is dealt with.

142
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,399
But Mr. Xiao,

143
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,860
you can sleep well tonight.

144
00:08:58,839 --> 00:09:01,740
Anyway, come back earlier tonight.

145
00:09:02,999 --> 00:09:04,380
Got it.

146
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,519
Mr. Lin.

147
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,679
Your white sportswear

148
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,039
is shining under the sun.

149
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,718
You look like an NPC.

150
00:09:32,719 --> 00:09:34,478
Didn't you promise to be the model

151
00:09:34,479 --> 00:09:36,139
of my NPC before this?

152
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,998
I was afraid that you might be busy.
That's why I'm doing this now.

153
00:09:38,999 --> 00:09:40,159
I can be your model at any time

154
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:42,220
as long as you need it.

155
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,840
You don't need to take pictures of me.

156
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,439
Really?

157
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,998
Will you sit still

158
00:09:45,999 --> 00:09:47,419
and let me finish the template?

159
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:49,358
You're so nice.

160
00:09:49,359 --> 00:09:50,740
It's a promise, then.

161
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,700
You suck at photography.

162
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:08,399
Isn't this pretty good?

163
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,939
Alright. I'll be there immediately.

164
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,878
David has agreed to see us.

165
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:15,598
Let's go.

166
00:10:15,599 --> 00:10:16,539
Okay.

167
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,838
This shouldn't be a major issue.

168
00:10:33,839 --> 00:10:36,358
However, it's kind of complicated.

169
00:10:36,359 --> 00:10:38,439
How long will it take for you to fix it?

170
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:41,740
The game concept launch event
will be held two days from now.

171
00:10:42,119 --> 00:10:44,279
It'll take me at least two to three days

172
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,838
provided that I can work together

173
00:10:45,839 --> 00:10:47,460
seamlessly with Goddess Lanyao.

174
00:10:48,959 --> 00:10:49,980
Alright.

175
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,439
You guys should finish it
as soon as possible.

176
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:55,059
Leave the rest to me.

177
00:10:57,479 --> 00:10:59,958
You and Ran have already
given them your guarantee.

178
00:10:59,959 --> 00:11:01,118
At this crucial moment,

179
00:11:01,119 --> 00:11:03,899
I mustn't allow the board of directors
to doubt you.

180
00:11:03,959 --> 00:11:06,679
And, it's only
the game concept launch event.

181
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,319
It's not the launch

182
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,878
of the full game.

183
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:10,878
I believe

184
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,700
that you'll achieve it.

185
00:11:13,119 --> 00:11:13,958
Alright.

186
00:11:13,959 --> 00:11:15,539
I'll surely do my best.

187
00:11:15,999 --> 00:11:17,059
You can do it.

188
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:21,340
You're finally here to visit me.

189
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:24,478
I've been too busy lately.

190
00:11:24,479 --> 00:11:26,899
How's your game doing?

191
00:11:28,599 --> 00:11:30,179
(What a stubborn man.)

192
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,958
We've located the key to fix the bug.

193
00:11:32,959 --> 00:11:35,500
Brother is meeting David
with our game designer.

194
00:11:35,999 --> 00:11:39,580
Xiao Ran, it's important
to always keep your guard up.

195
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,539
Dad, he's my brother.

196
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:42,799
He's your son too.

197
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,580
We're a family, you know?

198
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:46,139
Speaking of family,

199
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:49,600
how's your consideration?

200
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:52,320
Have you decided on whether you want
to marry the Shen family's daughter?

201
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:56,460
You mean Xiangyu and I?

202
00:11:56,719 --> 00:11:58,238
How many times have I told you before?

203
00:11:58,239 --> 00:11:59,860
I just treat her as my elder sister.

204
00:12:00,239 --> 00:12:03,998
About that, once we return to our hometown,
your mother and I will meet her parents.

205
00:12:03,999 --> 00:12:05,118
The marriage will be arranged

206
00:12:05,119 --> 00:12:06,279
if there are no objections.

207
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,758
It's my marriage. I'll make my own call.

208
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:09,299
You think you're all grown up, huh?

209
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:10,939
Mr. Xiao.

210
00:12:11,999 --> 00:12:12,519
Yunfei.

211
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,500
Mr. Xiao.

212
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,899
How do you feel?

213
00:12:15,959 --> 00:12:17,419
I feel great.

214
00:12:17,719 --> 00:12:18,919
It's just that someone is here

215
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,958
to make me angry.

216
00:12:20,959 --> 00:12:21,838
I don't know

217
00:12:21,839 --> 00:12:24,419
how long this body of mine
can withstand it.

218
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:28,199
Dad, please take care.

219
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,500
I love you the most.

220
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,159
What's wrong?

221
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,638
Did you not sleep well lately?

222
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:38,259
You look quite pale.

223
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,100
Why are you looking for me?

224
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:43,559
You're pretty close

225
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:45,358
to Goddess Lanyao lately, right?

226
00:12:45,359 --> 00:12:49,419
I wish to inquire about
her best friend, Liu Yiyi.

227
00:12:49,839 --> 00:12:53,019
I wish to know about her interests.

228
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:57,299
You like Liu Yiyi, huh?

229
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:01,539
Alright.

230
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:10,030
(Restoring)

231
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,980
We're finally almost done.

232
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,740
How is it?

233
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,878
How's the progress with the virus?

234
00:13:22,879 --> 00:13:24,559
I think we can complete it before dawn.

235
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:26,958
Ms. Song does live up to her reputation.

236
00:13:26,959 --> 00:13:29,480
Not only does she pick things up quickly,
but she's also very good at them.

237
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,740
That means you guys can finish it
one day before the deadline, huh?

238
00:13:32,479 --> 00:13:34,059
Lanyao, you're amazing.

239
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,700
It's because David is a great teacher.

240
00:13:42,719 --> 00:13:44,419
Seems like our goddess is starving.

241
00:13:45,119 --> 00:13:47,659
Come. Let's have a meal together.

242
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:50,598
But the virus is...

243
00:13:50,599 --> 00:13:52,799
It'll take over an hour
for the process to finish.

244
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:54,238
You guys shouldn't wait here.

245
00:13:54,239 --> 00:13:55,958
You can finish it
after having your meal.

246
00:13:55,959 --> 00:13:56,838
Go now.

247
00:13:56,839 --> 00:13:57,838
Aren't you joining us?

248
00:13:57,839 --> 00:13:59,039
Nope.

249
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,799
I have other jobs that I need to finish.

250
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,700
I'll use this opportunity
to finish them.

251
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,539
You guys can enjoy yourselves.

252
00:14:04,599 --> 00:14:05,500
Alright.

253
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:07,100
We'll come back after the meal.

254
00:14:07,119 --> 00:14:08,259
Go now.

255
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,860
Why isn't she back yet?

256
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:32,539
No.

257
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,838
If I call her right now,

258
00:14:34,839 --> 00:14:36,779
she'll definitely think
that I fancy her.

259
00:14:38,999 --> 00:14:41,779
Didn't I tell her to come back earlier?

260
00:14:43,479 --> 00:14:45,159
Don't tell me she fell asleep?

261
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:47,259
What if she transforms again?

262
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:58,500
Don't tell me it's because
the bed is uncomfortable?

263
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:24,100
I'm sure that's the case.

264
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,980
It's delicious indeed.

265
00:15:36,839 --> 00:15:38,358
We only spent 15 minutes

266
00:15:38,359 --> 00:15:40,019
to finish all of our food.

267
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:42,919
This should be the fastest meal I had

268
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:45,159
since my birth.

269
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:46,799
It's because Father taught us

270
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,700
to chew our food slowly.

271
00:15:48,999 --> 00:15:50,159
I heard

272
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:53,179
that you and Xiao Ran have
the same father but a different mother.

273
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,340
That's right.

274
00:15:54,759 --> 00:15:56,899
My mother remarried into the Xiao family

275
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,380
when I was three.

276
00:16:00,239 --> 00:16:04,939
If so, are you still in touch
with your biological father?

277
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:06,860
No.

278
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,700
Now, I only remember

279
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:11,179
Father, which is Mr. Xiao.

280
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:15,740
If so, is your relationship with him...

281
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:17,319
I mean...

282
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,460
I know.

283
00:16:21,879 --> 00:16:24,580
When my mother was still around,

284
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:28,139
even though he didn't
speak with me much,

285
00:16:28,719 --> 00:16:31,539
he smiled often.

286
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,620
But he rarely smiled

287
00:16:35,359 --> 00:16:37,259
ever since

288
00:16:38,479 --> 00:16:40,340
my mother had passed away.

289
00:16:43,599 --> 00:16:47,059
