to be closer to him.

290
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,700
I guess so.

291
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:59,620
But he wasn't willing
to acknowledge my existence.

292
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:06,979
I'm working so hard

293
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:09,300
to preserve this family.

294
00:17:10,399 --> 00:17:12,179
I truly hope

295
00:17:13,199 --> 00:17:14,820
that he can acknowledge my effort.

296
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,580
Even

297
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:20,060
a simple phrase of acknowledgment

298
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:23,100
or an expression of acknowledgment

299
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:25,100
would make me feel

300
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:28,139
that everything I did for the family

301
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:30,739
was worth it.

302
00:17:32,879 --> 00:17:34,158
When I was young,

303
00:17:34,159 --> 00:17:35,739
my parents were also...

304
00:17:36,599 --> 00:17:37,739
Forget it.

305
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,118
As the saying goes,

306
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:41,039
"People are born to suffer."

307
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:43,999
Since it's already tough enough
to stay alive,

308
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,198
why shouldn't we live happily

309
00:17:46,199 --> 00:17:48,398
for our own sake when we're alive?

310
00:17:48,399 --> 00:17:49,598
Just like now.

311
00:17:49,599 --> 00:17:50,999
I invested all of my savings

312
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,719
into this game
without my family's knowledge.

313
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,780
I would've starved had you guys

314
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:58,780
not invested in my game.

315
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,799
However,

316
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:03,118
my dream will be fulfilled

317
00:18:03,119 --> 00:18:05,139
when the game is fully online.

318
00:18:05,439 --> 00:18:08,198
If so, I think all the hardships
I endured were worth it.

319
00:18:08,199 --> 00:18:09,739
It'll make me happy.

320
00:18:10,359 --> 00:18:11,158
Therefore,

321
00:18:11,159 --> 00:18:13,939
I hope that you can
stop suppressing yourself.

322
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:16,279
You should express your love to Mr. Xiao

323
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:18,899
and work hard for
the sake of your happiness.

324
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:28,559
Alright.

325
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:32,659
I'll try my best to head
in that direction.

326
00:18:34,839 --> 00:18:36,139
Let's forget about me.

327
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:38,020
Let's talk about my brother.

328
00:18:39,439 --> 00:18:41,580
According to my knowledge of Ran,

329
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,899
I'm sure he's making you live with him

330
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:47,499
for some special reasons.

331
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:49,039
(Indeed.)

332
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:51,780
(But I can't tell you about it.)

333
00:18:52,839 --> 00:18:54,719
Isn't it obvious?

334
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:57,780
He's just afraid
that I might run away from work.

335
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:00,020
He thinks I'm a deadbeat.

336
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:04,219
You're different indeed.

337
00:19:04,679 --> 00:19:06,039
You see, Ran has female fans

338
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:08,300
everywhere.

339
00:19:09,359 --> 00:19:11,438
I even heard that he's considered

340
00:19:11,439 --> 00:19:15,979
a highly sought-after bachelor
in the outside world.

341
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,878
(Highly sought-after?)

342
00:19:18,879 --> 00:19:21,540
(More like highly sinister.)

343
00:19:23,919 --> 00:19:26,398
Alright. It's almost time.

344
00:19:26,399 --> 00:19:27,939
I'll send you back to David's place.

345
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:28,719
Alright.

346
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:30,260
Time to continue my work.

347
00:19:52,119 --> 00:19:54,300
Ms. Song, what's wrong with you?

348
00:19:55,439 --> 00:19:56,759
I stayed up all night for work.

349
00:19:56,760 --> 00:19:57,559
Uncle Xiang, I'm fine.

350
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,759
Just ignore me.

351
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,198
You haven't taken breakfast yet, right?

352
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:02,158
- I'll tell Ms. Qi to make you some...
- It's fine.

353
00:20:02,159 --> 00:20:02,959
I've taken breakfast.

354
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:04,179
Please proceed with your day.

355
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,118
Okay.

356
00:20:05,119 --> 00:20:06,239
Uncle Xiang.

357
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:08,020
Is Xiao Ran upstairs?

358
00:20:08,439 --> 00:20:10,060
Mr. Xiao is at the company.

359
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:13,020
Usually, he's at the company at this hour.

360
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,540
Mr. Xiao, you're home?

361
00:20:16,639 --> 00:20:18,580
Why didn't you tell me in advance
that you were back?

362
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:21,459
I would have no idea that you were back
if I didn't call Lin Qiao.

363
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:22,759
You stayed up all night.

364
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:25,559
