a disabled person after fixing the bug?

365
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:26,979
Or do you intend...

366
00:20:35,439 --> 00:20:38,860
Or do you intend
to transform at my house

367
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:41,219
and kill everyone?

368
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:44,519
I'm working tirelessly based upon

369
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:46,838
the hardworking etiquette
that Party B has to uphold.

370
00:20:46,839 --> 00:20:48,899
You came down

371
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,780
just when I was able to call you.

372
00:20:59,679 --> 00:21:01,739
