376
00:21:09,919 --> 00:21:12,780
But I can't sleep like this.

377
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,899
If so, you can report
your work progress to me.

378
00:21:14,919 --> 00:21:17,659
Tell me about last night's process.

379
00:21:36,399 --> 00:21:38,419
The launch event is nearing.

380
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:40,279
If we can

381
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:42,239
launch the game successfully,

382
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,918
