383
00:21:44,919 --> 00:21:47,598
Xiao Ran's position in the company.

384
00:21:47,599 --> 00:21:49,860
There's no way to destabilize him.

385
00:21:51,199 --> 00:21:52,158
Once the game is launched,

386
00:21:52,159 --> 00:21:54,319
all of you will be satisfied.

387
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:57,279
