are you guys unsatisfied with?

388
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:58,838
It's nothing.

389
00:21:58,839 --> 00:22:00,979
I just feel sorry for you.

390
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:03,079
You're very capable.

391
00:22:03,080 --> 00:22:04,719
You're the one dealing with

392
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,239
most of the company's affairs,

393
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,999
yet you're always below Xiao Ran.

394
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,079
That's right.

395
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:10,559
In my opinion,

396
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:13,039
you're the most suitable candidate

397
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,979
to be the company's CEO.

398
00:22:16,399 --> 00:22:17,120
What a shame.

399
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:19,640
If only you could establish a
marriage alliance with the Shen family.

400
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,620
Uncle Chen,

401
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:24,878
some of your statements
are quite inappropriate, don't you think?

402
00:22:24,879 --> 00:22:26,678
How is that so?

403
00:22:26,679 --> 00:22:28,079
We can help you out

404
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,239
if you have an idea.

405
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:32,260
We already had a plan all along.

406
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:36,620
However, we don't get
to decide what to do here.

407
00:22:36,919 --> 00:22:38,499
It depends on Mr. Lin's call.

408
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:43,419
If we do receive everyone's support,

409
00:22:43,639 --> 00:22:47,499
I'm sure the chairman will treasure him.

410
00:22:52,639 --> 00:22:54,179
Xiao Ran is my brother.

411
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,358
I will support him

412
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:56,979
no matter what happens.

413
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:58,598
Directors, you two don't need

414
00:22:58,599 --> 00:23:01,260
to worry about this.

415
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,319
Xiao Ran can definitely provide you two

416
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:05,380
with the things you two want.

417
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,899
However, if you two
have ulterior motives,

418
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:11,239
I'm afraid he won't agree to
your conditions that easily.

419
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,979
Lin Qiao.

420
00:23:13,119 --> 00:23:14,820
- You're...
- Uncle Li.

421
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:16,580
Have some tea.

422
00:23:40,480 --> 00:23:42,100
Mr. Xiao,

423
00:23:42,119 --> 00:23:44,820
